Package: igraphlite
Title: Lightweight R Interface to Igraph Network Analysis Library
Version: 0.10.12
Authors@R:
    person(given = "Watal M.", family = "Iwasaki", role = c("aut", "cre"), email = "heavywatal@gmail.com", comment = c(ORCID="0000-0002-4718-7605"))
Description:
    This is an Rcpp-powered R package interface to igraph network analysis
    library. It is not a fork of the existing R igraph package, but a reboot
    from scratch striving for good performance, simple codebase, and the
    consistency with the C implementation.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://heavywatal.github.io/rigraphlite/, https://github.com/heavywatal/rigraphlite
BugReports: https://github.com/heavywatal/rigraphlite/issues
Encoding: UTF-8
Roxygen: list(markdown = TRUE)
RoxygenNote: 7.3.1
SystemRequirements:
    CMake (>= 3.18.0), glpk, gmp, libxml2
Depends:
    R (>= 4.2.0)
LinkingTo:
    cpp11
Imports:
    generics (>= 0.1.3),
    rlang (>= 1.1.3)
Suggests:
    ape,
    ggplot2,
    testthat (>= 3.2.1)
Config/testthat/edition: 3
